Date: 1993-09-22

Title: On the Class of Possible Nonlocal Anyon-Like Operators and Quantum

GroupsAuthors: M. Chaichian, R. Gonzales Felipe, C. Montonen

Comments: 10 pages (plain latex), HU-SEFT R 1993-9, to be published in Journal

Journal-ref: J.Phys. A26 (1993) L1117-L1124

We find a class of nonlocal operators constructed by attaching a disorderoperator to fermionic degrees of freedom, which can be used to generateq-deformed algebras following the Schwinger approach. This class includes therecently proposed anyonic operators defined on a lattice.